## 2) What Our App Currently Does

StudentBridge is a web platform that helps international students in Korea find part-time jobs easily.

- Feature / flow 1: User can register an account using the registration form.
- Feature / flow 2: User can login using email and password.
- Feature / flow 3: User can browse and search jobs using filters (location, category, type).

### Current MVP flow

Our main user can:

1. Open homepage
2. Click register and create account
3. Login using credentials
4. Search and view job listings

